cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as relation classification. "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) is also a likely sub-category as the paper proposes a deep neural network architecture for the task. "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with the use of neural networks for a specific AI task. "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible sub-category as the paper proposes a deep recurrent neural network architecture. Finally, "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) is a less likely sub-category as the paper deals with the classification of relations between entities, which is a task related to information extraction.
